import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { Shield, Search, Package, AlertCircle, Eye, AlertTriangle, Download } from 'lucide-react'; const ReturnAnomalyPage = () => { const [selectedAlert, setSelectedAlert] = useState(null); const [filterRiskLevel, setFilterRiskLevel] = useState('all'); const returnAnomalies = [ { id: 'RA001', customerId: 'C987654321', pattern: 'High-value return abuse', returnCount: 12, timeframe: '30 days', totalValue: '$4,567.89', riskScore: 94, category: 'Serial Returner', title: 'High-value return abuse', riskLevel: 'High', description: 'Customer initiated 12 returns in 30 days', investigationBrief: 'Analysis shows consistent pattern of returns within 24-48 hours of purchase, primarily on electronics and designer items. Payment methods vary but shipping addresses remain consistent.', riskIndicators: ['high_value_returns', 'short_ownership_period', 'multiple_categories', 'frequent_returns'], subAgentResults: { 'Behavior Analysis': { score: 89, confidence: 'High' }, 'Payment Analysis': { score: 72, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Address Verification': { score: 95, confidence: 'High' }, 'Device Fingerprinting': { score: 83, confidence: 'High' } } }, { id: 'RA002', customerId: 'C456789012', pattern: 'Cross-category return pattern', returnCount: 8, timeframe: '14 days', totalValue: '$1,234.56', riskScore: 76, category: 'Suspicious Pattern', title: 'Cross-category return pattern', riskLevel: 'Medium', description: 'Multiple returns across different product categories in short timeframe', investigationBrief: 'Customer has returned items from electronics, clothing, and home goods categories within a 2-week period. Returns cite various reasons but follow similar timing patterns.', riskIndicators: ['cross_category_returns', 'compressed_timeframe', 'varied_reasons'], subAgentResults: { 'Behavior Analysis': { score: 76, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Payment Analysis': { score: 68, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Address Verification': { score: 82, confidence: 'High' }, 'Device Fingerprinting': { score: 71, confidence: 'Medium' } } }, { id: 'RA003', customerId: 'C123456789', pattern: 'Seasonal return abuse', returnCount: 15, timeframe: '45 days', totalValue: '$2,890.45', riskScore: 88, category: 'Seasonal Abuse', title: 'Seasonal return abuse', riskLevel: 'High', description: 'Consistent pattern of returns after seasonal events', investigationBrief: 'Customer shows pattern of purchasing high-value items before holidays/events and returning them immediately after. Items are typically in categories like formal wear, electronics, and jewelry.', riskIndicators: ['seasonal_timing', 'event_correlation', 'high_value_items', 'pristine_condition_returns'], subAgentResults: { 'Timing Analysis': { score: 92, confidence: 'High' }, 'Category Analysis': { score: 84, confidence: 'High' }, 'Condition Assessment': { score: 78, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Purchase Pattern': { score: 88, confidence: 'High' } } }, { id: 'RA004', customerId: 'C555666777', pattern: 'Bulk return processing', returnCount: 6, timeframe: '7 days', totalValue: '$899.99', riskScore: 65, category: 'Bulk Returns', title: 'Bulk return processing', riskLevel: 'Low', description: 'Multiple items returned in bulk within short period', investigationBrief: 'Customer returned 6 different items within a week, all from the same order. Returns appear legitimate but the volume and timing warrant monitoring.', riskIndicators: ['bulk_processing', 'same_order_returns', 'compressed_timeframe'], subAgentResults: { 'Order Analysis': { score: 62, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Return Reasons': { score: 58, confidence: 'Low' }, 'Item Condition': { score: 75, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Customer History': { score: 64, confidence: 'Medium' } } } ]; // Apply filters const filteredAlerts = returnAnomalies.filter(alert => { const riskLevelMatch = filterRiskLevel === 'all' || alert.riskLevel === filterRiskLevel; return riskLevelMatch; }); // Get unique categories for filter dropdown const handleAction = (id, action) => { console.log(`Action taken on ${id}: ${action}`); // Add actual implementation here }; // Calculate stats from the return anomalies data const stats = { totalAlerts: returnAnomalies.length, highRisk: returnAnomalies.filter(a => a.riskLevel === 'High').length, mediumRisk: returnAnomalies.filter(a => a.riskLevel === 'Medium').length, lowRisk: returnAnomalies.filter(a => a.riskLevel === 'Low').length, totalAmount: returnAnomalies.reduce((sum, alert) => { const amount = parseFloat(alert.totalValue.replace('$', '').replace(',', '')); return sum + (isNaN(amount) ? 0 : amount); }, 0), avgRiskScore: Math.round(returnAnomalies.reduce((sum, alert) => sum + alert.riskScore, 0) / returnAnomalies.length) }; return (

Return Anomaly Detection

Monitoring unusual return patterns and potential abuse

High Risk

{stats.highRisk}

Medium Risk

{stats.mediumRisk}

Avg Risk Score

{stats.avgRiskScore}%

Total Value

${stats.totalAmount.toLocaleString()}

{filteredAlerts.map((anomaly) => (
setSelectedAlert(anomaly)} className="cursor-pointer bg-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-5 border border-neutral-600 hover:border-neutral-400 hover:bg-neutral-600 transition" >

{anomaly.id}

{anomaly.riskLevel}

{anomaly.pattern}

{anomaly.description}

Customer ID: {anomaly.customerId}
Amount: {anomaly.totalValue}
{anomaly.timeframe} ago
Risk Score: = 90 ? 'text-red-400' : anomaly.riskScore >= 70 ? 'text-yellow-400' : 'text-green-400' }`}> {anomaly.riskScore}%
))}
); }; const InvestigationPanel = ({ selectedAlert, handleAction }) => { const getRiskColor = (riskLevel) => { switch (riskLevel) { case 'High': return 'bg-red-600/90 text-white border-red-400'; case 'Medium': return 'bg-yellow-500/90 text-black border-yellow-400'; case 'Low': return 'bg-green-500/90 text-white border-green-400'; default: return 'bg-neutral-700 text-white border-neutral-600'; } }; return (

Investigation Details

{selectedAlert ? (

{selectedAlert.title}

{selectedAlert.riskLevel} Risk

{selectedAlert.description}

Investigation Brief

{selectedAlert.investigationBrief}

Risk Indicators

{selectedAlert.riskIndicators.map((indicator, index) => ( {indicator.replace(/_/g, ' ').toUpperCase()} ))}

Sub-Agent Analysis

{Object.entries(selectedAlert.subAgentResults).map(([agent, result]) => (
{agent.replace(/([A-Z])/g, ' $1').trim()}
{result.score}%
{result.confidence} Confidence
))}
) : (

No Alert Selected

Select an alert from the dashboard to view investigation details

)}
); }; export default ReturnAnomalyPage;
